channel.title: Looking for a source!
channel.description:
Hello! I'm looking for a good source to start with my own server. I don't want to do a pk server. I'm looking a simple source which has only some skills working (att, def, str, hp). Also ::char command would be good.
I need this kind of source because I want to do my server skills with tutorials :). Thanks.
